      "field": "['after_hours_flow_summary']",
      "type": "updated",
      "old_value": "Calls are taken by Clara and routed appropriately based on urgency and business rules.",
      "new_value": "After hours, Clara answers and lets the caller know that Ben's Electric Solutions is currently closed. She then asks if the call is an emergency. If it is, she follows the emergency routing procedures. If it is not an emergency, Clara takes the message, gets all the details, and lets the customer know that the team will be in touch by 10 AM the next business day. The message is sent to Ben and Dave immediately.",
